lead_paragraph: On the first day of workouts, new Memphis Grizzlies coach David Fizdale approached point guard Mike Conley and told him he wanted him to be more aggressive scoring the ball this season.

headline.print_headline: Conley, Grizzlies Top Hornets 105-90 for 5th Straight Win
